--- How to test and build Hippo Site Toolkit ---

-- Requirements --

* Java 1.5
* Maven 2.0.9 

3. Testing

$ mvn clean install -Dmaven.test.skip=true
$ mvn org.apache.portals.jetspeed-2:jetspeed-mvn-maven-plugin:mvn -Dtarget=test

You can simplify the above command by adding the following in your settings.xml:

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<settings xmlns="http://maven.apache.org/POM/4.0.0">
  <pluginGroups>
    <pluginGroup>org.apache.portals.jetspeed-2</pluginGroup>
  </pluginGroups>
</settings>

Now, your command can be like this:

mvn jetspeed:mvn -Dtarget=test

4. Build

mvn clean install

